&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree. Preferred Fields of Study: Life Sciences or Engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 10 years of experience in a biopharmaceutical or related environment in an engineering or quality related role, with at least 5 years in a leadership role&lt;/li&gt;
