&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Validation Lifecycle (GAMP 5) principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with calibration and maintenance management software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of electronic do

